title: Mysteries of the Mekong Series 1 Part 01 China The Journey Begin
description: Mysteries of the Mekong Series 1 Part.01 China: The Journey Begins Nature Documentary hosted by Leila Monks, published by LoveNature in 2018 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/d/dd/Mysteries-of-the-Mekong-Series-1-Part.01-China-The-Journey-Begins-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Mysteries of the Mekong Series 1 Part01 China: The Journey Begins The journey of the Mekong River takes us through China, Laos, Vietnam, Cambodia, and Thailand, across a series of diverse landscapes. Each has its own signature species: from snub-nosed monkeys to high-flying birds, to spooky cave-dwellers--including some that have never been filmed before. The Yunnan Province in China marks the first leg in the 2,700-mile journey of the Mekong River. Fed by countless tributaries and glacial meltwater, it traverses the land it helped shape, Join us as we map the path of this mightiest of rivers.
